<tal:macro xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
           xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
           metal:use-macro="view.base_template">

<tal:slot metal:fill-slot="content">
<section id="main-content">

    <p>
        You have a variety of options in order to contact us. If you want
        to engage with the larger community or are comfortable discussing
        your request in the open, please use either:
        <ul>
            <li>
                <a href="https://lists.mozilla.org/listinfo/dev-geolocation">
                    Our public mailing list</a> or
                <a href="http://groups.google.com/group/mozilla.dev.geolocation">
                    view an online archive of the discussions</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                or join the #geo channel on
                <a href="https://wiki.mozilla.org/IRC">
                    Mozilla's IRC network</a>.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </p>

    <p>
        If your inquiry should stay private, you can contact
        <a href="mailto:Hanno Schlichting %3Chschlichting@mozilla.com%3E">
            Hanno Schlichting</a>,
        who will help you direct your question to the right audience.
    </p>

    <p>
        In the unlikely event that you want to raise a formal legal
        question, our address is:

        <pre>
            Mozilla Corporation
            Attn: Legal Notices
            331 E. Evelyn Ave.
            Mountain View, CA 94041
            Phone: +1-650-903-0800
        </pre>
    </p>

</section>
</tal:slot>

</tal:macro>
